        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n@Morgan, would you happen to know why ansible \"get_url\" is not storing helm3 as a tarball and instead is storing it as a text?\nFor now, this shell solution is ugly but unblocks Sylvain on one of the helm issues. \n\nWould you mind providing your review please?",
